The area within which METRO may collect sales tax.

Established in August 1978 and amended to include only "Full Purpose" annexations (or deannexations) by included local cities.

Includes Harris County 2013 annexation ordinance no. 2012-738 dated October 30, 2012

Includes Fort Bend County 2013 deannexation ordinance no. O-12-38 dated October 26, 2012.
